    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid opportunity for someone who wants an affordable driver or light project with good bones. This car shows cosmetic wear and age, but the powertrain pulls through the rev range, starts reliably, and the chassis still feels composed on the road. A practical platform with plenty of life left for the next owner who appreciates mechanical simplicity and easy wrenchability. Not perfect, but a straightforward, usable car that can be enjoyed as-is while you sort the finer details. Clean, honest value for the money.",
