    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of personality, this car has the kind of road-worn charm that makes every glance feel like the start of a story. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who appreciates character over cookie-cutter polish\u2014a great fit for a hands-on driver, weekend tinkerer, or anyone looking for an affordable way into something with soul. If you\u2019ve been searching for a budget-friendly ride with presence, potential, and plenty of opportunity to make it your own, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical opportunity for a budget-minded buyer, first-time owner, or hands-on project enthusiast. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who values low upfront cost and real potential over perfection. A sensible choice for basic transportation, a backup vehicle, or a restoration starting point.",
      "price": 4950.0,
