      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runabout that could make a great cheap commuter, learner car, or weekend project. If you\u2019re handy or just need something affordable to get started, there\u2019s real value here. Priced to sell and ready for someone who can give it a bit of TLC.",
      "price": 5800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project car with strong enthusiast bones and a drivetrain that still shows good character. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission goes through the gears, and the chassis feels like a worthwhile platform for a budget build, commuter revival, or weekend wrenching project. Cosmetic wear, age-related flaws, and general needs are present, so it\u2019s not a turnkey example, but for the right buyer this is an affordable entry point with real mechanical potential. Priced to move for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
